You're welcome! I'm glad I could help. Remember to be confident in your abilities and experiences, but also be humble and respectful in how you present them. It's great that you're taking the initiative to improve your skills and contribute to a team.

By sharing your previous experience and achievements, you'll be able to showcase your skills and demonstrate your commitment to the league. Just make sure to focus on how you can contribute to the team's success, rather than just highlighting your individual achievements.

If you have any more questions or need further guidance, feel free to ask. Good luck with your registration and your upcoming season!
